<script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org/","@type":"Product","@id":"https://hananuts.com/hat-chia/#product","name":"H\u1ea1t chia (500g)","url":"https://hananuts.com/hat-chia/","description":"&amp;#x2705; H\u1ea1t Chia (Salvia hispanica) l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1t nh\u1ecf m\u00e0u \u0111en ho\u1eb7c tr\u1eafng, c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1edd h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1, protein, axit b\u00e9o omega-3 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng.\r\n&amp;#x2705; Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng: Trong 100g h\u1ea1t chia ch\u1ee9a: Ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1: Kho\u1ea3ng 34g \u2013 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a, gi\u00fap no l\u00e2u. Omega-3: Kho\u1ea3ng 17g \u2013 t\u1ed1t cho tim m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 n\u00e3o b\u1ed9. Protein: Kho\u1ea3ng 16g \u2013 cung c\u1ea5p n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u00fap x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp. Canxi, Magie, Photpho, S\u1eaft: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 x\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eafc kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch.\r\n&amp;#x2705; C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1ea1t chia: T\u1ed1t cho tim m\u1ea1ch: Omega-3 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m cholesterol x\u1ea5u v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 tim. C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00ed nh\u1edb: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a n\u00e3o b\u1ed9. T\u1ed1t cho x\u01b0\u01a1ng: Cung c\u1ea5p canxi gi\u00fap x\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eafc kh\u1ecfe. L\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p da: Ch\u1ee9a ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba l\u00e3o h\u00f3a. H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n: Nh\u1edd ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u00e8m \u0103n.\r\n\r\n----------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n&amp;#x2705; T\u1ed4NG KHO H\u1ea0T DINH D\u01af\u1ee0NG \r\n&amp;#x2705; Chuy\u00ean s\u1ec9 - l\u1ebb h\u1ea1t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c\r\n&amp;#x2705; \u0110C kho 1: X\u00e3 Qu\u1ea3ng Ti\u1ebfn - Huy\u1ec7n C\u01b0 M'gar - T\u1ec9nh \u0110\u0103k L\u0103k\r\n &amp;#x2705; \u0110C kho 2: X\u00e3 H\u1ea3i T\u00e2n - Huy\u1ec7n H\u1ea3i H\u1eadu - T\u1ec9nh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh\r\n &amp;#x2705; TEL: 0985.528.613 ( Zalo/Call )\r\n&amp;#x2705; TEL: 0973.557.521 ( Zalo/Call )\r\n &amp;#x2705; Fanpage: https://www.facebook.com/hananuts68\r\n &amp;#x2705; Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 shop \u1ea1! \r\n\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Hana Nuts c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u1ea1!","image":"https://hananuts.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/si-hat-chia-gia-tot.jpg","sku":600,"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"5.00","reviewCount":1},"review":[{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","ratingValue":"5","worstRating":"1"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"vfqozoyxy"},"reviewBody":"H\u00e0ng \u1ed5n gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1t n\u00ean mua","datePublished":"2025-08-31T10:43:43+07:00"}],"brand":"Hana Nuts","mpn":null,"id":600}</script>
